{"tid":1150553,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我正大光明係老母面前倒左佢碗湯","createTime":"2019-05-12T02:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T10:33:55.000Z","uid":8883,"like":20,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"98f88ebb963910e22c37eab4b699168daf1659d2","tid":1150553,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"話說頭先我打緊lol個陣<br />\n我老母無端端捧碗湯入黎叫我飲左佢<br />\n咁打緊lol又點分神飲湯 咁咪話一陣飲<br />\n點知我老母5分鐘入黎煩我一次<br />\n最後我頂唔撚順係佢面前倒晒佢碗湯落地下<br />\n跟住佢眼濕濕扮委屈咁拖返乾撻地 我心諗你一開始唔好咁煩咪得囉 你逼我飲我就係都唔飲呀你吹咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家喊到佢豬頭咁"},{"pid":"4a356ccf93263800ea71776e442040a5810181c6","tid":1150553,"uid":133473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"咁又點?"},{"pid":"13da741b399788a1dd33486309e9224ed91e9841","tid":1150553,"uid":38775,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"樓主禿頭"},{"pid":"61cb33bfffeed7f364e459277e079ad66538da7c","tid":1150553,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:50:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母甘都做得出？你係人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefc60bdfca9be676fe794f509d3ef4e9f49754a","tid":1150553,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"係男人就成煲倒"},{"pid":"130995579e7d4cee76373e0b6f41eb92203e7466","tid":1150553,"uid":38189,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母碗湯係有助生髮，你咁都倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8727795b099c1aca5cf0cb9b4317061ee0510334","tid":1150553,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"係喇係喇叻喇叻喇知你好撚勁"},{"pid":"f3f1f8db616047bd9db644ed4a91bca59